snippet.title: Rogue Spirit 505 Games Announcement Trailer [ESRB]
snippet.description:
Rogue Spirit, an anime inspired 3D action-adventure game developed by Wrocław, Poland based studio Kids With Sticks, will be published worldwide by 505 Games! For more info on this exciting project, head on over to Steam or the 505 Games website. 

🎮 Playable demo coming June 9th to Steam
🎮 Early Access release this August
🎮 Wishlist here: http://505.games/RogueSpiritAnnounceYT
